        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4381725048" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1688064421388578696">After one of my friends recently reviewed this book, I went straight out to my library to get a copy. What I found was this 1966 Random House hardcover edition with slipcase. What a wonderful story for such a slim volume. It&apos;s autobiographical in nature and tells the story of seven-year-old Truman, known as Buddy and his aging distant cousin, &apos;Miss Sook&apos; during &quot;fruit cake weather.&quot; This is a splendid tale which boldly underscores the spirit of giving at Christmas time. A must-read during the ap</span>
  <span id="freeText1688064421388578696" style="display:none">After one of my friends recently reviewed this book, I went straight out to my library to get a copy. What I found was this 1966 Random House hardcover edition with slipcase. What a wonderful story for such a slim volume. It's autobiographical in nature and tells the story of seven-year-old Truman, known as Buddy and his aging distant cousin, 'Miss Sook' during "fruit cake weather." This is a splendid tale which boldly underscores the spirit of giving at Christmas time. A must-read during the approach of Christmas.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1688064421388578696" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

